  <walkingGeneralDescription><![CDATA[<p>On an Inghams walking holiday, you have the freedom to explore the area at your own pace. Each day, a new adventure, with as much or as little walking as you like.</p>
<h3>Why we love walking in Kamnik</h3>
<p>Kamnik is a perfect mixture of nature and sightseeing, so you can experience a lot whilst exploring on foot - whether it's a walk to some castle ruins, a wander through the ancient Velika Planina mountain pastures, or a visit to the botanical gardens, there's so much to see that you'll not notice the number of steps you're doing on the way. This is where the Slovenian's come on holiday, so you know it's going to be good.</p>]]></walkingGeneralDescription>
